并用固体冰填满山谷.

56
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:37,330
Its leading edge is called Gaumukh,the cow's mouth,
它的前缘叫Gaumukh,牛的嘴,

57
00:04:37,330 --> 00:04:40,910
as the water which flows under its vast icy tongue
就像是在其冰冷的舌头下流淌的水一样

58
00:04:40,910 --> 00:04:41,863
is milky white.
是乳白色的.

59
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:49,423
Hindus consider this to be the source of the Ganges.
印度教徒认为这是恒河的源头.

60
